    "The discrete torsion ψ in M(H, ψ) is introduced in the half-gauging picture for the H-gauge fields.",
    "This is the direct generalization of the usual fixed point resolution in ordinary orbifold[103] for both local operators and defects.",
    "Here we have used that Rep(H8) ∼ = Rep(H8) op, which is obvious from its fusion rules and F-symbols.",
    "For example, the corresponding module category for trivial gauging (i.e.",
    "A = 1) is C itself."
